"O - The Bruery's 7 Swans-A-Swimming is a beautiful addition to their 12 Days of Christmas series and is one of the most well-done American-brewed Belgian Quads, right on for ""style"" - something they rarely seem to shoot for. Malty, complex, and loaded with classic Belgian yeast characteristics, this big beer will surely hang on for the remainder of the series, developing over time!"
